name: Moto Moto
description:
MotoMoto is a fast paced endless runner with a twist. High risk high reward, the closer your are to the top of the screen,  the less time you'll get to dodge incoming obstacles but you'll get a great score multiplier.  Play as you wish ! DOWNLOAD IT ON GOOGLE:
